title: Dolphins Swimming
description: The image shows two dolphins swimming gracefully in clear blue water. The larger dolphin is swimming above, while a smaller dolphin is swimming just below the surface, creating a beautiful contrast against the shimmering water.

title: Sea Turtle Swimming
description: A sea turtle gracefully swimming through a vibrant underwater scene filled with colorful corals and marine plants.

title: Underwater Scene
description: The image depicts a vibrant underwater scene divided into two parts: the above-water area featuring a seagull perched on a rock, and the underwater area showcasing various marine life. The underwater section includes colorful corals, a jellyfish, a starfish, a crab, and several fish swimming among seaweed and rocks. The background features a serene ocean with distant land visible.

title: Underwater Scene with Eel
description: An underwater image showcasing a vibrant marine environment. In the foreground, there are long green seagrass blades swaying gently in the water. Among the seagrass, a moray eel is partially visible, peeking out from its hiding spot. The background features a clear blue ocean with small fish swimming around, creating a lively underwater scene.
